      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELEVENTH SCOTCH (1) was below best at his last start when 8th at Healesville following a win (22.62) at this track two back. Has ability and looks hard to stop. MORAINE MILEY (2) has been in sparkling form, last time breaking from this same box to win a Bottom Up - Grade 5 at this track (22.48) and making it two straight wins. Expecting another bold showing. MORAINE ARNIE (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing eighth (22.91) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 at this track. Form here at the trip sound including eight wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and nine minor placings. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. FRED'S FURY (5) returns here with a good chance to improve on last time.",
